data.enText: a small bomb that can be thrown by hand or fired from a gun

tr: a small explosive bomb thrown by hand or fired from a missile

value.def: A grenade or a hand grenade is a small bomb that can be thrown by hand.

example.ex: A hand grenade was thrown at an army patrol.
example.tran: 一枚手榴弹掷向了陆军巡逻队。

trans: 杀伤榴弹(爆炸时迸射出大量碎片)
眩晕弹，震撼手榴弹(使人无法动弹但不会造成重创)
